criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Aged 30-60 years old male and female;
2. 2 deputy chief physician diagnosed chloasma;
3. Facial skin intact, no obvious inflammation, ulceration, exudation;
4. No facial filler such as hyaluronic acid or laser/light treatment;
5. No oral steroids, collagen powder/liquid, or topical hyaluronic acid used in the last 3 months;
6. No skin whitening products in the last 2 weeks.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Pregnant or in breast-feeding peroid;
2. Facial dermatitis patients;
3. Allergic to trial medcine or its ingredient;
4. Have severe cardiovascular, cerebrovascular, renal, hepatic or hematopoietic disease;
5. Poor coagulation function;
6. Taking part in other clinical trials;
7. People that researchers believe they are not suitable to participate in the study.
